<F P=100> SOUTH ASIA </F>
<F P=101> Afghanistan </F>
<H3> <TI>   Golboddin-Dostum Militia Fires 250 Rockets on Kabul </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Golboddin-Dostum Militia Fires 250 Rockets on Kabul </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0505174694 Kabul Radio Afghanistan Network in Pashto 1530 
GMT 5 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0505174694 </F>
<F P=104>  Kabul Radio Afghanistan Network </F>
<F P=105>  Pashto </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Last night, Golboddin-Dostam militia fired 250 
rockets and mortar shells into the residential areas of Kabul. 
According to a source of Kabul City Garrison Command, as a 
result of the rocket attack, three residents of Kabul were 
martyred and six others were injured. Similarly as a result of 
the last night's rocket attack, a dwelling was destroyed, and a 
number of shops were damaged in the city center. The source 
added that today too, Golboddin-Dostam militia fired rockets 
into some areas of Kabul. No report about the loss of life and 
material damage has been received. 

</TEXT>

