and lives of its sons. It hoped that logic and wisdom will 
prevail as a means to overcome the acute crisis in the country. 
  An authoritative source at the Foreign Ministry has told the 
Kuwaiti News Agency that Kuwait is watching with concern the 
regrettable development of the situation in the Yemen Republic 
and is urging Yemeni brothers to exercise self-restraint to end 
the fighting and spare the blood and lives of the country's sons. 
  The source has added: Kuwait is hoping that logic and wisdom 
will prevail in order to overcome this acute crisis. 

