<F P=102> NC0505143994 Paris AFP in English 1420 GMT 5 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0505143994 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris AFP </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Sanaa, 5 May (AFP) -- All-out fighting erupted 
Thursday in Yemen between rival troops in seven provinces as 
five southern warplanes were shot down, a northern military 
spokesman said here. 
  The spokesman told the official news agency SABA' that 
southern forces from Aden had suffered heavy losses in clashes 
with northern troops in seven of Yemen's 17 provinces. 

