<DOCNO> FBIS4-58701 </DOCNO>
<HT>    "drnes088dd_94002" </HT>


<HEADER>
<AU>   FBIS-NES-94-088 </AU>
Daily Report 
<DATE1>  5 May 1994 </DATE1>

</HEADER>

<F P=100> Palestinian Affairs </F>
<H3> <TI>   Al-Husayni Put in Charge of `Jerusalem Portfolio' </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Al-Husayni Put in Charge of `Jerusalem Portfolio' </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   TA0505172894 Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el in English 1500 GMT 5 
May 94 </F>

<F P=103> TA0505172894 </F>
<F P=104>  Jerusalem Qol Yisra'el </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] In Jerusalem, Palestinian leader Faysal al-Husayni 
says he has been appointed to take charge of the Jerusalem 
portfolio on behalf of the PLO. 
  He said he did not take part in yesterday's signing ceremony 
for two reasons. He had hoped the accord would be more 
positive, and he was busy at work. 

</TEXT>

