<H3> <TI>   Security Forces Ordered To Prepare for Deployment </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Security Forces Ordered To Prepare for Deployment </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   NC0505164294 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1520 GMT 5 May 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0505164294 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 5 May (MENA)--Palestinian President Yasir 
'Arafat has issued an order for the Palestinian national police 
and security forces to prepare to move immediately to take up 
their positions in Gaza and Jericho. 
  This was stated to MENA by Zuhdi al-Qidrah, acting 
Palestinian ambassador in Cairo and Fatah's representative. He 
said that 'Arafat issued this order following the signing of the 
agreement on the implementation of Palestinian self-rule in Gaza 
and Jericho in Cairo yesterday. 

</TEXT>

