<H3> <TI>   Foreign Ministry Welcomes Cairo Self-Rule Agreement </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foreign Ministry Welcomes Cairo Self-Rule Agreement </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0405200694 Tunis Tunis-7 Television in Arabic 1900 GMT 4 
May 94 </F>

