  [Text] President Yasir 'Arafat yesterday received Russian 
Foreign Minister Andrey Kozyrev, who conveyed to him the 
congratulations of the Russian president, government, and people 
on the signing of the peace agreement. 
  Mr. Kozyrev stressed the Russian Federation's support for 
the 
efforts of re-building the political, economic, and 
administrative infrastructure of the Palestinian National 
Authority. 
  President Abu-'Ammar ['Arafat] asked Kozyrev to convey his 
thanks to President Boris Yeltsin for the efforts he has been 
making toward the establishment of the Palestinian National 
Authority. 

