<H3> <TI>   Foreign Ministry Condemns Interference in Yemen </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foreign Ministry Condemns Interference in Yemen </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0705150194 Tehran IRIB Television First Program Network in 
Persian 1430 GMT 7 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0705150194 </F>
<F P=104>  Tehran IRIB Television First Program Network </F>
<F P=105>  Persian </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Iran has expressed deep regret about internal 
clashes in Yemen. 
  A spokesman of our country's Foreign Ministry today called 
on 
the warring sides in Yemen to maintain their self-control, 
observe Islamic principles, and find peaceful ways to solve 
their differences. 
  He also condemned foreign interference in the escalation of 
crisis in Yemen and announced the readiness of the Islamic 
Republic of Iran to help towards solving the differences and 
maintaining the Yemen unity. 

</TEXT>

