<F P=102>   LD0805172594 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1700 
GMT 8 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0805172594 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Radio Algiers Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The security services announced today that two 
French nationals, aged 64 and 67, who were running a bookshop 
were assassinated by gun fire from armed men at about 1500 hours 
at Benchleb Street in El Casba quarter. 
  The security services also said that its forces had cordoned 
off the area and had begun the search for the perpetrators of 
the crime. 

</TEXT>

