through the Arab world. Do you know anything about the fate of 
the missing Israeli servicemen? 
  [Al-Shaqaqi] You know, I think all the Israeli 
soldiers, except Ron Arad, are dead. 
  [Sherzer] Do you know that for a fact? 
  [Al-Shaqaqi] Yes, for a fact. 
  [Sherzer] Nowadays he and his wife and two children live in 
Damascus. He teaches his four-year-old daughter about the 
Palestinian cause. In his opinion, the Gaza-Jericho agreement 
is a disaster. [passage omitted] [end recording] 

