BFN 

  [Text] The U.S. assistant secretary of state for Middle 
East affairs made a statement in Amman yesterday in which he 
disclosed the U.S. Administration's determination to interfere 
in the events witnessed in Yemen. He described what is taking 
place there as civil war, and talked about what he called 
military victories and the determination to fight in these 
