<F P=104>  Sanaa Yemeni Republic Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

<F P=106> [Presidential Council Decree No. 21 issued on 9 May -- read </F>
by announcer] 
  [Text] The chairman of the Presidential Council, cognizant 
of the Constitution of the Republic of Yemen, and upon the 
recommendation of the acting prime minister, in view of the 
requirements of public interest, and after the approval of the 
President Council, decrees the following: 
