appointed minister of defense. 
<H5>  Article II. </H5>
  This decree will be valid as of date of issue and will be 
published in the official gazette. 
  Issued at the Presidency in Sanaa on 29 Dhu al-Qi'dah, 1414 
of the hegira, 9 May 1994. 
  [Signed] Lieutenant General 'Ali 'Abdallah Salih, chairman 
of 
the President Council 
  Dr. Muhammad Sa'id al-'Attar, acting prime minister 

</TEXT>

