<H3> <TI>   France: Evacuation of Foreign Nationals Completed </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    France: Evacuation of Foreign Nationals Completed </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0905215194 Paris France-Inter Radio Network in French 2030 
GMT 9 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0905215194 </F>
<F P=104>  Paris France-Inter Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  French </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] With regard to the civil war in Yemen, the northern 
forces say they are about to take control of the former capital 
of the south, Aden. Most foreign nationals have now left the 
country. France led the operations from Djibouti. The [French] 
Defense Ministry announced in Paris this evening that the 
evacuation of foreign nationals by air or sea was now over. A 
total of 1,456 people left Yemen over the last few days, 
including 214 French citizens. 

</TEXT>

