  [Excerpt] The spiral of terrorism continues. The security 
services announced today that two citizens have been 
assassinated by two terrorists in the provinces of Boumerdes and 
Tiaret. 
  The imam of the Baghlia mosque in Boumerdes province was 
stabbed to death; his body was found near an elementary school 
in Bourj Menial municipality. Rached Benallou, 43 years old, 
who was the muezzin of El Rahouia in Tiaret province, was also 
murdered. [passage omitted] 

