<H3> <TI>   Economic, Social Council Members Announced </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Economic, Social Council Members Announced </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD0905175094 Algiers Radio Algiers Network in Arabic 1600 
GMT 9 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> LD0905175094 </F>
<F P=104>  Algiers Radio Algiers Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The composition of the executive bureau of the 
National Economic and Social Council was announced at the Palace 
of Nations a few moments ago. The council is composed of the 
following: 
  Mohamed Laid Anane, Abdelmadjid Sidi Said, Mustapha 
Mekideche, Mohamed Hamida, Abdeslam Bouchareb, Samia Belabbes, 
Hocine Ait Chaalal, Mehrez Ait Belkacem, and Mohamed Zaaf. 
  The council is under the obligation to be fully prepared and 
devoted to the job. The members of the council were chosen 
after long consultations. 

