<H3> <TI>   Bombs Explode at Officials' Homes in Sikkim </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Bombs Explode at Officials' Homes in Sikkim </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   BK0905102094 Delhi All India Radio Network in English 0830 
GMT 9 May 94 </F>

<F P=103> BK0905102094 </F>
<F P=104>  Delhi All India Radio Network </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] In Sikkim, two bombs exploded at the residence of 
the state power minister and the former chief secretary. The 
director general of police, Mr. P.S. Bawa, told PTI today that 
the power minister, Mr. B.B. Subba, was not at his residence 
when the explosion took place last night. Another bomb was 
hurled at the residence of the former chief secretary, Mr. P.K. 
Pradhan, in the early hours yesterday. The explosions, however, 
did not cause much damage. 

</TEXT>

